           MODULE=gaim-applet
         VERSION=0.59.6
       # VERSION=0.59.4
          SOURCE=gaim-$VERSION.tar.bz2
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/gaim-$VERSION
   SOURCE_URL[0]=$SFORGE_URL/gaim/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://gaim.sourceforge.net
         ENTERED=20020313
         UPDATED=20021107
           SHORT="gaim-applet is a Gnome panel applet version of gaim"
cat << EOF
gaim-applet, like gaim, is an instant messanger client used primarly for the AIM protocol
but has plugin support for icq, irc, yahoo, and jabber all at once
in one interface.  gaim-applet has the added ability to run in a gnome panel as a gnome applet.
EOF
